activate :i18n

# Requires:
#   locales/en.yml, locales/es.yml
#   source/localizable/files.html
localize [:en, :es], :path => "/:locale/", :root => "localizable", :lang_file_extensions => [".html"]

:lang_file_extensions
---------------------

By default middleman-i18n will only localize files containing _.html_, but
this behavior can be overridden by specifying the file extensions to include
in localization. For example, to localize both _.html_ and _.php_ files use
`:lang_file_extensions => [".html", ".php"]`.
